    "The softmax function used for probability distributions is given in Eq. 4.v c ¼ 1 S c j j X ðx i Þ2S c f h ðx i Þ ð 3Þ p y ¼ cjx ð Þ¼softmax Àd f h x ð Þ; v c ð Þ ð Þ ¼ expðÀdðf h x ð Þ; v c ÞÞ P c02C expðÀdðf h x ð Þ; v c0 ÞÞð4ÞHere, training is performed based on the cross entropy error of the query set instances in meta-training.",
    "The parameters of the f h backbone network are updated to minimize the loss values.Briefly, ProtoNets work by learning a prototype representation for each class in a way that minimizes the distance between the prototype and support examples (training images).",
    "In our application, ProtoNets were adapted to the medical image classification task by utilizing them to generate compact and discriminative representations of breast cancer lesions.",
